{"word":"τερατεύομαι","slug":"τερατεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τερατεύομαι</b></el> <el>(τερᾰτεύομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τέρας'><el>τέρας</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to talk marvels</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>portenta loqui</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>; <el>τ. τῷ σχήματι</el> <i>to indulge in marvellous</i> gesticulation, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/>"}]}